cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper deals with multi-object tracking using sensors such as cameras and lidars, which are commonly used in robotics and autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also focuses on autonomous vehicles, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with path planning and navigation, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
